sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as History or Graph Webview
participant Router as Feature Message Router
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as ResetCurrentBranchUseCase
participant Plans as OperationPlanRegistry
participant Worktree as Worktree
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime

User->>App: Reset current branch to commit
App->>Router: reset request(worktreeLocator, targetCommit)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>UseCase: plan(Worktree, targetCommit)
UseCase->>Worktree: getStatus()
UseCase->>Worktree: getReflog(first page)
UseCase->>Plans: store resetHard plan with preview hash
Plans-->>Router: planId
Router-->>App: guarded operation plan
User->>App: Acknowledge destructive preview
App->>Router: guarded acknowledgement(planId)
Router->>Plans: validate acknowledgement
Plans-->>Router: validated plan
Router->>UseCase: execute(validated plan)
UseCase->>Worktree: resetHard(targetCommit)
Worktree->>Runtime: resetHard(context, targetCommit)
Runtime-->>Worktree: success
UseCase-->>Router: recovery hint with previous HEAD
Router-->>App: operation success and refresh requested
